5 term not to exceed thirty (30) days, and by a fine not less than
6 Fifty Dollars ($50.00) nor more than Five Hundred Dollars ($500.00);
7 2. For a third or subsequent conviction, in the event the value
8 of the goods, edible meat, or other corporeal property which has
9 been taken is less than One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00) Five
10 Hundred Dollars ($500.00), the person shall be guilty of a
11 misdemeanor and shall be punished by imprisonment in the county jail
