20 not to exceed One Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00);
21 4. In the event the value of the goods, edible meat, or other
22 corporeal property is Two Thousand Five Hundred Dollars ($2,500.00)
23 or more but less than Fifteen Thousand Dollars ($15,000.00), the
24 person shall be guilty of a felony and shall be punished by
