3 Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00); or
4 5. In the event the value of the goods, edible meat, or other
5 corporeal property is Fifteen Thousand Dollars ($15,000.00) or more,
6 the person shall be guilty of a felony and shall be punished by
7 imprisonment in the custody of the Department of Corrections for a
